      code:`class MathHelper {\n    static int square(int n)   { return n * n; }\n    static int cube(int n)     { return n * n * n; }\n    static boolean isPrime(int n) {\n        if (n < 2) return false;\n        for (int i = 2; i * i <= n; i++)\n            if (n % i == 0) return false;\n        return true;\n    }\n}\n\nSystem.out.println(MathHelper.square(5));    // 25\nSystem.out.println(MathHelper.cube(3));      // 27\nSystem.out.println(MathHelper.isPrime(17));  // true\nSystem.out.println(MathHelper.isPrime(4));   // false`,
