      code:`static int longestSubarray(int[] arr, int target) {\n    int l=0, sum=0, maxLen=0;\n    for(int r=0;r<arr.length;r++){\n        sum+=arr[r];\n        while(sum>target) sum-=arr[l++];\n        maxLen=Math.max(maxLen, r-l+1);\n    }\n    return maxLen;\n}`,
